@node "TalesFromHeavenTechnics" "tales from heaven - Technical information"

TALES FROM HEAVEN
=================

Technical information:
----------------------

- Own software support for Converting and Texturing our objects.

  *K3D-Coverter*     Converts files of LightWave to K3D (our own format)
  *K3D-Texturizer*   Superb software for texturing easly (one year of development)
  *K3D-Background*   Generate awesomes 3d maps in a simple lookup-table
  *K3D-MapEditor*    For develop these marvellous maps in 3D

- Great system of collisions in 3d, we accurate 100% of speed in the latest time.

- 3D-Engine very very optimized (see yourself), we had working on it over two years.

- ZBuffer Horizont Clipping for smoothing the culling of polygons.

- Sprite Scaling support in all sizes.

- Transparencies.

- Multiple Backgrounds (scroll, 3d sphere or blue color).

- Easy mode of Animation Frames mode in 3D.

- Morph 3D.

- ArtificialInteligence in some enemies very advanced.

- Pixel mode for slow machines.


System Requeriments:
--------------------

at least:  AGA/68030, 8Mb ram, CD-Rom
recommended:  AGA/68040 or 68060, 16Mb, CD-Rom

